import Legal from '../layouts/Legal.astro';
---

<Legal title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for 7/16. Learn how we handle your personal information." locale="en">
  <h1>7/16 Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>

  <p>
    7/16 ("we", "us", or "the service") considers the proper protection of user personal information an important responsibility. This policy describes how personal information is handled within the service.
  </p>

  <h2>Use by Minors</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>This service is not intended for persons under 13 years of age.</li>
    <li>Persons under 16 should obtain parental consent before use.</li>
    <li>If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a person under 13, we will promptly delete it.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3>(1) Information You Provide</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Email address or phone number</li>
    <li>Username</li>
    <li>Date of birth</li>
    <li>Profile photo (optional)</li>
    <li>Bio (optional)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>(2) Photo Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Photos explicitly selected by the user</li>
    <li>Metadata necessary for functionality (file format, date taken, etc.)</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="note">We do not access or store your entire photo library.</p>
  <p class="note">Because the service includes a random selection feature, selected photos may be automatically shared after selection.</p>

  <h3>(3) Location Data</h3>
  <p>Collected only when the user chooses to share it. This can be changed in settings at any time.</p>

  <h3>(4) Automatically Collected Information</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address</li>
    <li>Device information (OS, model, app version, etc.)</li>
    <li>Usage logs (post times, view history, reaction history, etc.)</li>
    <li>Crash logs</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>(5) Information from Third Parties</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Hashed matching data when other users sync their contacts</li>
    <li>Statistical information from analytics providers</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Contact access requires the user's permission.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>

  <h3>(1) Service Delivery (Contract Fulfillment)</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Account creation and management</li>
    <li>Random photo selection and sharing features</li>
    <li>Push notifications</li>
    <li>Reaction features</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>(2) Fraud Prevention and Safety (Legitimate Interest)</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Detecting unauthorized use</li>
    <li>Enforcing terms of service</li>
    <li>Handling reports</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>(3) Service Improvement</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Usage analysis</li>
    <li>Bug fixes</li>
    <li>Performance optimization</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>(4) Advertising and Marketing (With Consent Only)</h3>
  <p>If advertising is introduced in the future:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Ad delivery</li>
    <li>Effectiveness measurement</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Consent may be withdrawn at any time.</p>

  <h3>(5) Legal Compliance</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Fulfilling legal obligations</li>
    <li>Responding to courts and law enforcement</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-Party Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not share personal information with third parties without consent, except as required by law.</p>
  <p>Exceptions include:</p>

  <h3>(1) Service Providers</h3>
  <p>Cloud providers, analytics providers, and others engaged under appropriate contracts.</p>

  <h3>(2) Business Transfers</h3>
  <p>In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale.</p>

  <h2>International Transfers</h2>
  <p>When transferring personal information outside Japan, we implement appropriate safeguards in accordance with applicable data protection laws.</p>

  <h2>Retention Period</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Information is retained only as long as necessary for the stated purposes.</li>
    <li>After account deletion, deletion processing begins within 15 days as a general rule.</li>
    <li>This does not apply where retention is required by law.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Security Measures</h2>
  <p>We implement the following measures to prevent leakage, loss, or damage of personal information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Encrypted communications</li>
    <li>Access restrictions</li>
    <li>Minimal data collection</li>
    <li>Internal access controls</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Under applicable law, you may request:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access to your data</li>
    <li>Correction</li>
    <li>Deletion</li>
    <li>Suspension of use</li>
    <li>Withdrawal of consent</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:info@stormstory.jp">info@stormstory.jp</a></p>
  <p>Identity verification may be required.</p>

  <h2>Social Sharing Considerations</h2>
  <p>This service includes social sharing features.</p>
  <p>Once content is shared, it may be saved or re-shared by other users. We cannot fully control third-party saving or redistribution.</p>

  <h2>Policy Changes</h2>
  <p>This policy may be updated as needed. We will notify you of significant changes in advance.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    7/16 Operations<br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:info@stormstory.jp">info@stormstory.jp</a>
  </p>
</Legal>
